headline.print_headline: 2 Stabbed to Death Outside Texas Skating Rink
headline.main: 2 Stabbed to Death Outside Texas Skating Rink

lead_paragraph: Two men were stabbed to death and several other people wounded in a fight early Saturday outside a North Texas roller skating rink, officials said.
